<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>选股标准制定 - YTC Trader</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/modern-premium.css">
    <style>
        body { background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0a0a0f 0%, #0f172a 50%, #0a0a0f 100%); min-height: 100vh; }
        .hero-section { text-align: center; padding: 60px 20px; background: radial-gradient(ellipse at top, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, transparent 50%); }
        .hero-title { font-size: 3rem; font-weight: 800; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #06b6d4 100%); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; }
        .content-section { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 40px 20px; }
        .card { background: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); border: 1px solid rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.2); border-radius: 16px; padding: 32px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
        .card::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, #6366f1 0%, #06b6d4 100%); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
        <!-- 科技光晕背景层 -->
        <div class="tech-glow"></div>

    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1 class="hero-title">选股标准制定</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content-section">
        <div class="card">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">趋势标准</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
                <li>周线上升趋势</li>
                <li>价格在50日均线上方</li>
                <li>价格在200日均线上方</li>
                <li>近期创52周新高</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">质量标准</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
                <li>行业龙头或细分龙头</li>
                <li>业绩稳定增长</li>
                <li>财务健康</li>
                <li>有核心竞争力</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <h2 style="margin-bottom: 20px;">流动性标准</h2>
            <ul style="color: var(--text-secondary); line-height: 2;">
                <li>日均成交额 > 5亿</li>
                <li>市值 > 100亿</li>
                <li>换手率适中</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
